document_data.mainbody: The '''High Rise''' was one of the districts of the city of [[Sambral]].
document_data.Geography: The largest and most diverse district, the High Rise was the center of commerce in Sambral. Three large gates allowed entrance to this district, and the High Market, as well as the popular temple of [[Tempus]], were located there.
